Package: shadowfetch-defaults
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Shadowfetch Project <maintainers@shadowfetch.com>
Installed-Size: 21
Depends: fastfetch
Recommends: shadowfetch-themes, shadowfetch-branding, papirus-icon-theme
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://shadowfetch.com/linux/
Description: Shadowfetch default user configuration
 Ships the Shadowfetch defaults applied to new user accounts (via
 /etc/skel): kdeglobals, kwinrc, konsole profile, fastfetch config.
 Also ships a system-wide /etc/profile.d snippet that prints a
 fastfetch banner on the first interactive shell.
